Getafe would like to sign Real Madrid's Brahim Diaz on loan this summer, president Angel Torres has confirmed.<br />
<br />
&quot;Real Madrid know we're interested in him,&quot; Torres told Cadena COPE radio after Getafe's Europa League defeat to Inter on Wednesday. &quot;If they let us and he wants to come, we'll make room for him at Getafe.&quot;
